snippet.textDisplay:
Tiffany Haddish is just so personable, so relatable, she feels like she could be your best friend and would be the one to go to jail with you.

And Wendy, I'm pulling for a good 2020 for you. You've had to overcome a lot and doing it while working on sobriety... amazing.

I've got over three years clean after 12 years using opiates. You know, looking back, I'm just glad I'm alive.

When you're at your grandmother's, who had cooked dinner, and she comes back to your room and gets your plate because you've nodded out face first into it...rock bottom.

I spent last year caring for her from January til September. I'm so glad I was clean and able to have that time and now I humbly beam with pride when papaw or others recall how she called me her Superstar for caring for her.

It's still a raw emotion...time to watch this and get some humor to lift me up.
